			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">FIELD SCREEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Speak witrh other characters / Execute command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display the quick save window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display the menu screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">EVENT SELECTION SCREEN/CHRONICLE SCREEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move cursor fast:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Execute command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Scroll through the event selection screens/reverse years in the chronicle:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BATTLE SCREEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor / Switch / Equip weapons switch between the equipped items and equipped arts windows:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Execute command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change side of target cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display the party status screen (hp/lp):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
